high_descs: Walk straight ahead to the wall and then right to the kitchen table.
Pick up the remote control on the table.
Turn right and walk straight ahead to the ottoman.
Place the remote on the ottoman near the front right corner.
Turn left and walk to the TV.
Pick up the remote from the TV stand.
Turn around and walk back to the front of the ottoman.
Place the remote on the ottoman to the left of the other remote.
anns.task_desc: Place two remotes on an ottoman.

high_descs: move to the table to the left of the door

move to the ottoman to the left of the piano
put the remote on the ottoman
move to the TV stand to the left of you
pick up a remote from the TV stand
move to the ottoman to the left of the piano
put the remote on the ottoman
anns.task_desc: Put two remotes on a ottoman.

high_descs: Cross the room until you get to the trash bin in the corner and then turn right to walk to the corner of the table.
Pick up the remote control from the table.
Move around the table and when the wall on the right ends, turn right and continue into the room until you're standing in front of an ottoman.
Place the remote control on the ottoman.
Turn left and move to the television stand.
Pick up the remote control from beneath the television.
Turn around and carry the remote control to the ottoman.
Place the remote control to the left of the other one previously left on the ottoman.
anns.task_desc: Move two remote controls to the ottoman.
